snippet.title: Little Runmo The Game | Official Launch Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
Download available here: https://juhosprite.itch.io/little-runmo

Music used from the original Runmo OST also made by Gooseworx: https://youtu.be/GJTL-gvU8Bo?si=J-vEOUoORtnQMYBm

WATCH THE ORIGINAL: https://youtu.be/ErQHVUQ6QCk?si=hHU9LTQmfwm5R0Ko

Demo trailer: https://youtu.be/eg3BE4XTSGg?si=pgU5RjYpXtFBCr_l
Teaser trailer: https://youtu.be/3H1L8Tu8F3I?si=F8H59Fh-Vs8oMAzE

The game is now out, for free! You can play it on your Windows computer, or if you are using any other device, you can play the browser version!

If you want some more info about the game, we have a discord that holds all the development details that you would want to know about.

Discord: https://discord.gg/AenfJ7WQuf
